玩，成班泛民都柒撚慒慒無撚用。<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，雨革後對香港人都無乜期望，出街再望下啲細路，個個六六六操你媽B，香港嘅下一代都被洗腦蝗化到不得了，香港將來好難有出路。<br />\n<br />\n你舉牌係有guts，我欣賞你，但好多人(包括我)其實都已經麻木哂(正中中共下懷)。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31af6bb272782f3907d9cc09bfab3203e8f22f6","tid":1026913,"uid":81052,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"柒過左膠拎坐監黎講"},{"pid":"28ca9197b712b597ad588299fb9e5fe8879c7ab0","tid":1026913,"uid":219887,"like":8,"dislike":11,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:19:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c98e0bec682a8925c75ddbbf664e61e0d11ea42f","tid":1026913,"uid":175623,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:45:51.000Z","msg":"你愈嬲班賤種愈開心，明眼人會知你既付出"},{"pid":"4cf69df98c58827c4123ac4c02e345cb934d2c0c","tid":1026913,"uid":198583,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:08:47.000Z","msg":"支持范國威都唔支持你條傻佬啦"},{"pid":"4beb968b0125491f6808d2f00d6e4828e6f7e154","tid":1026913,"uid":49336,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c98e0bec682a8925c75ddbbf664e61e0d11ea42f","tid":1026913,"uid":175623,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T15:45:51.000Z","msg":"你愈嬲班賤種愈開心，明眼人會知你既付出"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"明眼人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jessicahk-uat-resources.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/files/gillian_cover_copy_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjessicahk-uat-resources.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ffiles%2Fgillian_cover_copy_0.jpg&h=86973774&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"876e154fc8dc0e05a47b821360ad1f8407a5e905","tid":1026913,"uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":8,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:13:19.000Z","msg":"雖然關sir好煩膠，但係啲五毛成日搵埋啲無厘頭藉口"},{"pid":"bb06a05193b9b6e93be2eb6fc11ccfbeae4d858c","tid":1026913,"uid":216477,"like":17,"dislike":5,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:13:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pi